## Key Commands

### EF Migrations
```powershell
cd services/common/StockTracker.Data.Migrations
dotnet run -- migrate     # Apply migrations
dotnet run -- status      # Check status
dotnet ef migrations add <Name>  # New migration
```

### Docker (Local with Infisical)
```powershell
# Inject secrets from Infisical and run docker-compose
infisical run --env=prod -- docker-compose up -d
docker-compose logs -f
```

### Azure VM Access
```powershell
# SSH to VM (PowerShell alias)
ssh-azure

# Or direct SSH with command (preferred for scripts/AI)
ssh -i "$HOME\.ssh\nx-linux-server-azure_key (1).pem" azureuser@20.17.176.1 "docker ps"

# Commands to run INSIDE the VM (after SSH):
docker ps                                    # List running services
docker logs <service-name>                   # View service logs
docker compose up -d --build <service-name>  # Rebuild service
```

### Service URLs
```
# n8n Dashboard
https://nxserver.malaysiawest.cloudapp.azure.com/

# TwelveData Swagger
https://nxserver.malaysiawest.cloudapp.azure.com/api/twelvedata/swagger

# Health Checks
https://nxserver.malaysiawest.cloudapp.azure.com/api/twelvedata/health/live
```

